public class TwoWayMap<X,Y>
extends Object

A bi-directional map X <-> Y. For lack of better terms (yes, we considered "domain" and "range") the map is between a set of Xs and a set of Ys.

Note that this class is not thread-safe.

Author:
Borislav Iordanov
